comments: Strengths- small size so discussion was robust and interesting, the material is super relevant, Professor is good at facilitating discussion, the readings are good. Weaknesses- the class only meets once a week so we have to fit a lot of material into each class.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would definitely recommend this course. I would always look forward to learning an incredible amount on Friday mornings.
